# Auto Marketplace - Car Listings Platform

A professional car marketplace web application built with PHP, MySQL, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, featuring server-side validation, API endpoints, and improved accessibility. Migrated from XML/DTD storage to MySQL for better performance.

