## Features

- **Desktop-First Design** – optimized for PC users  
- **Responsive Layout** – adapts to mobile and tablet  
- **Advanced Search & Filtering** – search by make, model, year, price  
- **Image Gallery** – multiple images per listing with thumbnail navigation  
- **Form Validation** – client & server-side validation with clear error messages  
- **Accessibility** – WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliant  
- **Security** – prepared statements, input sanitization, file upload validation  
- **API Endpoints** – RESTful API for search and listing operations  

---

## Technology Stack

### Frontend
HTML5, CSS3 (Grid/Flexbox), Vanilla JavaScript  

### Backend
PHP 7.4+ (PDO), MySQL 5.7+  

### Architecture
MVC Pattern, DAO Pattern, Prepared Statements

---

## Installation & Deployment

### Prerequisites

- PHP 7.4+  
- MySQL 5.7+ (or MariaDB 10.2+)  
- Web server (Apache, Nginx, or PHP built-in server)  
- Composer (optional)

### Local Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/auto-marketplace.git
cd auto-marketplace
cp config.example.php config.php
# Edit config.php with your database credentials
php -S localhost:8000

Access via browser: http://localhost:8000

Deployment with Apache/Nginx
cp -r * /var/www/html/auto-marketplace/
chmod -R 755 /var/www/html/auto-marketplace
chmod -R 777 /var/www/html/auto-marketplace/uploads

Configure VirtualHost (Apache example):

<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName auto-marketplace.local
    DocumentRoot /var/www/html/auto-marketplace
    <Directory /var/www/html/auto-marketplace>
        AllowOverride All
        Require all granted
    </Directory>
</VirtualHost>
Database Setup
CREATE DATABASE auto_marketplace CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

Import schema and optional seed data:

mysql -u your_username -p auto_marketplace < database/schema.sql
mysql -u your_username -p auto_marketplace < database/seed.sql
Configuration

Edit config.php:

define('DB_HOST', 'localhost');
define('DB_NAME', 'auto_marketplace');
define('DB_USER', 'your_username');
define('DB_PASS', 'your_password');

define('UPLOAD_DIR', __DIR__ . '/uploads/');
define('MAX_FILE_SIZE', 5 * 1024 * 1024); // 5MB
define('ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS', ['jpg','jpeg','png','gif','webp']);
define('DEBUG_MODE', false);
Use Cases & Testing
<details> <summary>Browse Car Listings</summary>

Steps: Navigate to index.php, view listings grid, click a card
Expected: Grid adapts to device, images load, details visible
Checklist:

 Grid layout displays correctly

 Images load properly

 Clicking a card shows detail page

 Responsive breakpoints work

</details> <details> <summary>Search by Make, Model, Year</summary>

Steps: Use search + filters
Expected: Shows only matching results, real-time updates
Checklist:

 Text search filters correctly

 Dropdown filters work

 Price filter works

 Multiple filters combine

 "No results" message shows when empty

</details> <details> <summary>Create New Listing</summary>

Steps: Fill form, upload 2-3 images, submit
Expected: Listing appears, form validates fields
Checklist:

 Required fields validated

 Image upload works

 Listing appears on homepage

 Success message displays

</details> <details> <summary>View Car Details</summary>

Steps: Click listing card
Expected: Image gallery, specs, price, contact
Checklist:

 Gallery displays correctly

 Thumbnails navigate main image

 All details visible

 Contact button works

</details> <details> <summary>Server-Side Search API</summary>

Endpoint: GET /api/search.php
Checklist:

 JSON response valid

 Filters work correctly

 Errors handled

</details>
API Endpoints
<details> <summary>Search API</summary>

GET /api/search.php
Parameters: q, makes[], years[], maxPrice, minPrice
Example:

curl "http://localhost:8000/api/search.php?q=Toyota&makes[]=Toyota&maxPrice=30000"
</details> <details> <summary>Listings API</summary>

GET /api/listings.php
Parameters: id (optional)
Example:

curl "http://localhost:8000/api/listings.php"
curl "http://localhost:8000/api/listings.php?id=car1"
</details>
Accessibility

WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliance

Visible focus states, ARIA labels

Alt text for all images

Keyboard navigation & skip links

Proper form labels

Migration Report

Migrated from XML/DTD to MySQL

Cars table & car_images table

ID preservation, image normalization, type conversion

New timestamps & display_order fields

Indexed for performance

AI Use Disclosure

Cursor AI & GitHub Copilot used

Human review on all AI-generated code

Final architecture & security decisions human-made

Security

Input validation & sanitization

PDO prepared statements

File upload validation (types & size)

Error messages do not expose info

Troubleshooting

Database connection issues → check config.php & MySQL

Image upload failures → check folder permissions & PHP settings

Search/API errors → verify data & endpoints

